A 61 year old Chinese national was apprehended on Friday at
Bredell  in Kempton Park by members of of  K9 for possessing unlicensed pistols together with different types of live
rounds. The Police acted on a tip off and on arrival at the man' s
premises, two pistols and different types of live rounds  were found on
the safe which was mounted on the wall. Later on further investigation, Kempton Park Police went to
the suspect' place again and found two hunting Rifles with live rounds . The suspect failed to produce the licenses for both
Firearms. He will appear in  the Kempton Park Magistrate Court
soon to face his charges.